<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1039044-i-don-t-get-the-big-twist-in-the-end">I don&#39;t get the big twist in the end... can anyone help me?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1039044'><a id="like_count_community_question_1039044" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1039044?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">28 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F32326398-sometimes-i-lie">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1039044-i-don-t-get-the-big-twist-in-the-end">4 years ago</a>
</li>
