<div id="review_2465356191" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2465356191" />
    <a title="Felicia" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/13169794-felicia"><img alt="Felicia" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1464034900p2/13169794.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2465356191?book_show_action=true">May 09, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Felicia" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Felicia" href="/user/show/13169794-felicia">Felicia</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/36112959-sometimes-i-lie">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2465356191" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14459667035500971458">I liken this story to a ride on Space Mountain at Disneyland. If you&apos;re unfamiliar with this iconic ride, it&apos;s an indoor rollercoaster IN THE DARK. <br/><br/>It&apos;s dark. <br/>It&apos;s thrilling. <br/>It&apos;s disorienting. <br/>And you never see the twists coming.<br/><br/>Even with all the hype, this book still exceeded my expectations. <br/><br/>4.5 Stars ⭐</span>
  <span id="freeText14459667035500971458" style="display:none">I liken this story to a ride on Space Mountain at Disneyland. If you're unfamiliar with this iconic ride, it's an indoor rollercoaster IN THE DARK. <br /><br />It's dark. <br />It's thrilling. <br />It's disorienting. <br />And you never see the twists coming.<br /><br />Even with all the hype, this book still exceeded my expectations. <br /><br />4.5 Stars ⭐</span>
