      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/52960112-sometimes-i-lie">Quotes from Sometimes I Lie</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Nana always said that books made better friends than people anyway. Books will take you anywhere if you let them, she used to say, and I think she was right.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/8470074-nana-always-said-that-books-made-better-friends-than-people">81 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;We are all made of flesh and stars, but we all become dust in the end. Best to shine while you can.&rdquo;</span>
